snippet.title: Star Quest: TCG Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Star Quest: TCG's trailer, by FrozenShard Games.
A Sci-Fi themed Trading Card Game that combines the compelling aspects of the strategy games and the fast-paced matches from the Card Games.
